Arena King-of-the-Hill task + spaced-out plots

- HubService: a "👑 King of the Hill" capture pad at the arena centre — stand on it
  (on foot) to earn a steady 70 coins/sec. Adds an active reason to hold the middle
  alongside the coin orbs.
- Spaced-out world: plots now sit 60 studs apart (drivable lanes between them)
  instead of edge-to-edge, and the shared ground + boulevard were widened to span
  the more spread-out plot row.

